/span><br />\n正派王道漫仍然有一群讀者支撐住<br />\n雖然比較新啲七原罪 在連登都好少討論<br />\n但五葉草在連登直頭好似無一個帖過二頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己講左啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人睇好正常 除非佢係6pages啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常新番點差法都會有人開帖，最多無乜人討論啫<br />\n五葉草話哂都係少年Jump嚟<br />\n但自從新番開播以來 連集中討論帖都無個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印象中七原罪做動畫個期都好多人討論嫁"},{"pid":"4830fd6b426f1ba9c7cf23c177873f6b2951cf3a","tid":437594,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/426502/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/426502/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0310927231c0ce642fd65ea6f6eb9ba7788d43e4","tid":437594,"uid":55375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"唔係冇人講"},{"pid":"3db388179aab363ac4135721e820ebf614b9591d","tid":437594,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/426502/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/426502/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok 我更正﹕除咗呢個帖"},{"pid":"b3590f968ee8c4ea78e236612a9c0256a79ccced","tid":437594,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"一齊睇吓外國啲評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">標題[閒聊] 黑色五葉草到底好看在哪</span><br />\n<br />\n沒有要戰才怪<br />\n<br />\n看到十幾話就棄追，雖然畫風、分鏡等方面都算中庸，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但劇情沒梗到不忍直視又是一個Underdog主角打臉全世界的物語，<br />\n<br />\n只是這次的包裝換成了魔法、騎士之類的東西<br />\n<br />\n當你以為主角是魔法劣等生...不！其實他是得到規格外魔法書《五葉草》的傢伙(ry<br />\n<br />\n而且又來個生世不明的孤兒，最後可想而知又是某某失落的血統</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">整體戲法套路玩不出什麼新花樣，論演出手法拙劣、論刻劃描繪淺薄<br />\n<br />\n融會的元素還真可謂東抄一點西抄一點，幾乎找不到自己的特色</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然中下還算可以看，但基本上連小品的素質都不到<br />\n<br />\n但是，為什麼這樣的作品，這禮拜已經看到兩個排行榜在推？<br />\n<br />\n難道是海水退了，其實是我沒穿褲子？<br />\n<br />\n現在是該搬出北靠岸，中台漫月刊兩大神作護法了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有沒有行家解說一下這部到底哪裡值得這樣推薦？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1455003733.A.D92.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FC_Chat%2FM.1455003733.A.D92.html&d=neYjx%2FrIBxYsJCp6Mxa9Acn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=550c8785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1455003733.A.D92.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>我認為只係一般王道漫畫啲套路<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">橙字</span>我認為係劣質王道漫路啲特徵 例如﹕妖尾"},{"pid":"8a1c026bb71e78928334afaab2c47b71ad4c25b0","tid":437594,"uid":115525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"尋晚睇左2集<br />\n第1集開始已經覺得亞斯塔 把死人聲同重複又重複既對白 煩到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第2集以為有D咩熱血野睇啦<br />\n仆街睇到15分鐘先回憶完 根本直接由修女講故仔再跳到去派信件事都得<br />\n成段15分鐘都係廢既<br />\n然後一刀就打完<br />\n<br />\n屌 我係咪睇緊死神濃縮版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93a6a3f4eb62b1e08cc55b4c876cac2ca6fbc3a","tid":437594,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"PTT 網友評價<br />\n<br />\nsarevork: 火影接班絕對神作你不信<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">註﹕黑色五葉草被譽為火影忍者啲接班人，受少年jump力捧</span><br />\n<br />\nDialysis: 就是一個&quot;偽廢材流&quot;的套路,主角根本開大外掛<br />\n<br />\ndoranobi0125: 王道老梗總是有人會喜歡<br />\n<br />\nhongyan: 真的就是一堆無聊的老梗走向"},{"pid":"de6eac67d1b9015c7eb472cd9f8c78fd09cc71f2","tid":437594,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>難以置信 垃圾都有人講</blockquote><br />\n咁講真個句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">始於各人口味不同</span><br />\n正派王道漫仍然有一群讀者支撐住<br />\n雖然比較新啲七原罪 在連登都好少討論<br />\n但五葉草在連登直頭好似無一個帖過二頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己講左啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇人睇好正常 除非佢係6pages啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正常</span>新番點差法都會有人開帖，最多無乜人討論啫<br />\n五葉草話哂都係少年Jump嚟<br />\n但自從新番開播以來 連集中討論帖都無個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印象中七原罪做動畫個期都好多人討論嫁</blockquote><br />\n你自己講左個問題出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1137464a50444662f132ee67fb66abe231f9d88b","tid":437594,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"聽到把聲就火滾<br />\n仲話追"},{"pid":"e72ce6f20aa267527828456184c52d9e1fa2de6e","tid":437594,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"睇多陣耳膜都穿，不了"},{"pid":"f03b512b82c66aa92104b575a0c6e201a8808a49","tid":437594,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"我鐘意魔法零蛋多d"},{"pid":"29ca9a8ed95c349c4a6d9031108599b70402f77c","tid":437594,"uid":93062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"配角好睇過主角系列"},{"pid":"fd6a3097cc120dcae4892ed0653166230786f636","tid":437594,"uid":55628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"首歌係幾好聽嘅"},{"pid":"dfac5c66ead100fac42b52956f309af6deb449ef","tid":437594,"uid":105